َ","translation":"সাহায্যপ্রাপ্ত হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_123_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76805,"position":19,"arabic":"١٢٣","translation":"(১২৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":124,"arabic":"۞ وَإِذِ ٱبْتَلَىٰٓ إِبْرَٰهِۦمَ رَبُّهُۥ بِكَلِمَٰتٍۢ فَأَتَمَّهُنَّ ۖ قَالَ إِنِّى جَاعِلُكَ لِلنَّاسِ إِمَامًۭا ۖ قَالَ وَمِن ذُرِّيَّتِى ۖ قَالَ لَا يَنَالُ عَهْدِى ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ","translation":"And [remember this:] when his Sustainer tried Abraham by [His] commandments and the latter fulfilled them, He said: \"Behold, I shall make thee a leader of men. \"Abraham asked: \"And [wilt Thou make leaders] of my offspring as well? \"[God] answered: \"My covenant does not embrace the evildoers.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/131.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":76994,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَإِذِ","translation":"এবং (স্মরণ করো) যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_124_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76995,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱبْتَلَىٰٓ","translation":"পরীক্ষা করেছিলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_124_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76996,"position":3,"arabic":"إِبْرَٰهِـۧمَ","translation":"ইবরাহীমকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_124_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76997,"position":4,"arabic":"رَبُّهُۥ","translation":"তার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/002_124_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76998,"position":5,"arabic":"بِكَلِمَـٰتٍۢ","translation":"কয়েকটা কথা দ্বারা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_124_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76999,"position":6,"arabic":"فَأَتَمَّهُنَّ ۖ","translation":"সে অতঃপর সেগুলো পূর্ণ করল","audioUrl":"wbw/002_124_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77001,"position":7,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(আল্লাহ্‌) বললেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_124_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77002,"position":8,"arabic":"إِنِّى","translation":"''নিশ্চয়ই আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_124_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77003,"position":9,"arabic":"جَاعِلُكَ","translation":"তোমাকে নিয়োগ করব","audioUrl":"wbw/002_124_01