, and those who will abide near it in meditation, and those who will bow down and prostrate themselves [in prayer].\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/132.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":77127,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذْ","translation":"এবং (স্মরণ করো) যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77128,"position":2,"arabic":"جَعَلْنَا","translation":"আমরা নির্দিষ্ট করেছলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77129,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْبَيْتَ","translation":"(কাবা) ঘরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77130,"position":4,"arabic":"مَثَابَةًۭ","translation":"মিলনকেন্দ্র","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77131,"position":5,"arabic":"لِّلنَّاسِ","translation":"মানুষের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77132,"position":6,"arabic":"وَأَمْنًۭا","translation":"ও শাস্তির (জায়গা হিসেবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77133,"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱتَّخِذُوا۟","translation":"এবং (নির্দেশ দিলাম) তোমরা গ্রহণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77134,"position":8,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77135,"position":9,"arabic":"مَّقَامِ","translation":"দাঁড়ানোর জায়গাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77136,"position":10,"arabic":"إِبْرَٰهِـۧمَ","translation":"ইবরাহিমের","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77137,"position":11,"arabic":"مُصَلًّۭى ۖ","translation":"সলাতের জায়গা হিসেবে''","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77139,"position":12,"arabic":"وَعَهِدْنَآ","translation":"এবং আমরা আদেশ করেছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77140,"position":13,"arabic":"إِلَىٰٓ","translation":"প্রতি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_125_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77141,"positio